<div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0066cc;">Add an Address</h3>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;">To add a new address to your account:</p>
  <ol style="margin-left: 20px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5em;">Send an email to <strong style="color: #000;">$nickname@postcardmailer.us</strong></li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5em;">Use <strong style="color: #000;">adduser</strong> as the subject line</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5em;">In the email body, include the recipient's name and address</li>
  </ol>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Example:<br>
    To: mom@postcardmailer.us<br>
    Subject: adduser<br>
    Body: Jane Smith<br>
    456 Oak Avenue<br>
    Chicago, IL 60601
  </p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><em style="color: #666;">Note: Our AI-powered address parser will automatically standardize and validate the address format to ensure accurate delivery through the US Postal Service.</em></p>
</div> 